				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\text{NDVI}=(\text{NIR}-\text{Red})/(\text{NIR}+\text{Red})$$\end{document}

Then, central to our analysis is the dimidiate pixel model17, a validated method used for calculating the FVC as per the Eq. (2) detailed below18.2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
