				\begin{document}$$\text{FVC }= \frac{(\text{NDVI}-{\text{NDVI}}_{\text{soil}})}{( {\text{NDVI}}_{\text{veg}}-{\text{NDVI}}_{\text{soil}})}$$\end{document}

In Eq. (2), NDVI measures vegetation density; NDVIsoil corresponds to the NDVI of non-vegetated areas, while NDVIveg relates to heavily vegetated zones. The calculations for both NDVIsoil and NDVIveg are executed as per Eqs. (3) and (4) outlined subsequently19.3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
